WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en-GB

00:00:03.120 --> 00:00:07.140
Looking for a dentist In Watford? Then here
is a short guide to help you choose a good

00:00:07.140 --> 00:00:09.519
dental practice.

00:00:09.519 --> 00:00:14.210
Your first considerations are probably location
and opening hours?

00:00:14.210 --> 00:00:19.680
If you live or work in Watford, choose a dentist
that is close and convenient. And make sure

00:00:19.680 --> 00:00:25.169
that they offer suitable opening hours. For
example, if you work in Watford Town Centre,

00:00:25.169 --> 00:00:30.189
would it be wise to choose a dentist located
on the other side of Leavesden? Or what happens

00:00:30.189 --> 00:00:34.320
if you have a dental emergency on a Sunday
morning? When will you be able to get into

00:00:34.320 --> 00:00:36.940
your dentist for treatment?

00:00:36.940 --> 00:00:44.210
Do they have the right professional qualifications?
Don’t be afraid to ask for a dentist's qualifications.

00:00:44.210 --> 00:00:50.710
A good professional practice will be only
too happy to show you. In fact all dentists,

00:00:50.710 --> 00:00:56.089
dental nurses, technicians, hygienists and
dental therapists must be registered with

00:00:56.089 --> 00:01:06.680
the UK’s regulatory body, the General Dental
Council. You can find out more at www.gdc-uk.org

00:01:06.680 --> 00:01:10.690
Will you feel comfortable?
Make sure you call or better still, visit

00:01:10.690 --> 00:01:15.910
the dental practice and see how you are treated.
Will you feel comfortable there? Are they

00:01:15.910 --> 00:01:21.410
polite and happy to help with good professional
advice? And if it would put your mind at rest,

00:01:21.410 --> 00:01:25.800
as well as talking to the reception staff,
ask to talk to the dentist and make sure you

00:01:25.800 --> 00:01:29.820
feel confident and relaxed when talking to
them.

00:01:29.820 --> 00:01:34.570
What are their practice standards?
The Watford dentist that you visit must be

00:01:34.570 --> 00:01:41.570
tidy, clean and organised. All the staff should
be welcoming, friendly and respectful. A good

00:01:41.570 --> 00:01:46.030
practice will be open and honest with pricing
and be able to offer you a clear plan and

00:01:46.030 --> 00:01:48.970
estimate for the work that they carry out.

00:01:48.970 --> 00:01:56.930
Does this dental practice offer additional services?
Will this Watford dentist offer appointment reminders, additional

00:01:56.930 --> 00:02:02.850
dental advice in a written or video format?
Do they pay special mind to children and teach

00:02:02.850 --> 00:02:08.590
them about long term dental health? Or maybe
English isn’t your first language, so is

00:02:08.590 --> 00:02:12.920
this dentist able to speak your language or
has staff that can translate.

00:02:12.920 --> 00:02:17.799
There is a good choice of dentists in the
Watford, who are situated from the town centre

00:02:17.799 --> 00:02:29.300
out to more local areas. So, be sure that
you make the right choice.

